reviewText: This was an exceptionally designed online course for the beginner through to an experienced online teacher such as myself. I was particularly grateful for the reference lists and resources lists that I have mined to create a reading list for myself for the next few months and also to try new programs/applications as I grow in my skills. There are multiple examples that provide inspiration for different things you could try.

I​ learnt about the immersion of technology and education and how best educator can use technological tools like Zoom to improve learner online engagements. I would recommend this course to any educator leaning towards online teaching.
G​reat resources in which to build from.
The discussion was well organized and the course instructor was very engaging and ethusiastic all through out!
